cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper discusses the potential of Information-Centric Networking (ICN) for Internet of Things (IoT) environments. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses security and caching approaches, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses operating systems and simulation tools, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
